'desc': [u'

Wear Your Opinion Men's Round Neck T-Shirt Price: Rs.314

Add some charm to your elegant personality by wearing this casual T-shirt from Wear Your opinion. Crafted from 100 per cent cotton
column17:
this yellow T-shirt has a round neck and comes with pigment prints at the front to give a cool casual look. The half sleeves on this slim fit shirt add on to your elegance.

\r\n

\r\n\tTeam this Wear Your Opinion Yellow T-shirt with a pair of chinos and loafers for a vivacious look on a weekend getaway with your loved ones. Accessorize this attire with a funky belt and put on a pair of sunglasses to complete this attire with a touch of flamboyance.\xa0A cutting edge brand that permits the modern young men to showcase his individualistic persona
column18:
Wear Your Opinion comes out with impressive T-shirts which could easily steal your heart.

Fabric care

Machine wash this T-shirt inside out in warm water to retain the freshness of the fabric. Avoid bleaching. Refrain from ironing on the print and use warm iron inside out.
